Jennifer White-Johnson bụ ónyé na-ese ihe na ónyé na-eme ngagharị iwe bi na Baltimore. Dị ka onye na-ese ihe Afro-Latina nwéré nkwarụ na ADHD na Graves' Disease ọ na-eji ihe osise na foto dị ka ụzọ isi kwurịta njikọ nke ikike ndị nwere nkwarụrụ na mmegide agbụrụ, yana inye ọhụụ màkà olu ndị na-ezighị ezi. Mgbe ọ nwetasịrị MFA ya na Graphic Design site na Maryland Institute College of Art, o nweela ohere iso ọtụtụ ụdị, [promotion?] ma kụzie dị ka prọfesọ nke Visual Communication Design na Mahadum Bowie State
Ụfọdụ n'ime ọrụ ya a ma ama [dubious  gụnyere akara Black Disabled Lives Matter, na zine Black Autistic Joy advocacy zine a na-akpọ Knox Roxs.
White-Johnson nwetara BA yá nà Visual Arts na Mahadum Maryland Baltimore County
O nwèkwàrà MFA na Graphic Design site na Maryland Institute College of Art

White-Johnson bụ ugbu a [mgbe?] bụ prọfesọ nke Visual Communications na Mahadum Bowie State, ébé ọ bụ ónyé ndụmọdụ ngalaba ụmụ akwụkwọ màkà ngalaba Bowie State nke American Institute of Graphic Arts (AIGA). Ọ rụkwara ọrụ maka ụdị ndị gụnyere Nike, Converse, Twitter, Amazon, Today at Apple, na Google Stories, na-atụle ma na-emepụta ihe omume gbụrụ-gbúrụ njikọ nke nka na nkwarụ. N'afọ 2019, ọ bụ onye nnọchiteanya na mmemme 5 Points nke akpọrọ "Olee otu esi abụ onye Black Designer na-enweghị mfu mkpụrụ obi gị". N'afọ 2020, White-Johnson bụ onye a na-asọpụrụ na D-30 Disability Impact List maka nka mkpesa ya na atụmatụ mgbochi ịkpa ókè agbụrụ, na 2021 e gosipụtara ya na ndepụta nke ndị Latino Artists 20 iji lelee site na Today Show.
